            <ul style="color:red;">
                <li>Loan Request and Approval</li>
                <li>Loan Disbursment by Accountant</li>
                <li>Loan Report</li>
                <li>Loan Proofs Setup</li>
                <li>Loan Types Configuration</li> 
                <li>Loan Policy Configuration</li>
                <li>Repayment of Loan by Payroll - Intergrated with Payroll System</li>
                <li>Repayment of Loan by Cash/Bank</li>
                <li>Disbursment using Cash/Bank or Payroll</li>
                <li>Loan Installments and Booking Interest and Booking entry if repayment method = cash/bank</li>
             </ul>
        </p>
